Business Summary


Manufactures electric power suppliesAcBel Polytech, Inc. is engaged in the researching, developing, designing, manufacturing, and selling of power supply.Its other activities include the manufacturing and selling of communication and electronic components, market researching of power supply, processing and manufacturing of hardware, and provision of investment services.The firm's products include open frame power supply, server power supply, storage power supply, telecommunication power supply, power line communication, light emitting diode (LED) lighting, power line communication, smart metering system, backup power, and other related products.The company was founded on July 29, 1981 and is headquartered in New Taipei City, Taiwan.
 





