Follow the Millennials
For Maximum Revenue Growth
 
Private Equity Investing
In Food & Nutrition Companies


                                      
CHAIRED BY
Sarah Ashmore Bradley, Founding Partner 
  Kainos Capital LLC
 
MARQUEE SPONSOR
Parthenon-EY 
 
