Headquarters
London, United Kingdom


Revenue
 GB£232.5 million (2016)[1]



Net income

 GB£128.7 million (2016)[1]


AUM
 US$52.6 billion (2016)[1]


Total equity
 GB£128.7 million (2016)[1]



Number of employees

266 (2016)[1]


Website
www.ashmoregroup.com


Ashmore Group plc (LSE: ASHM) is a large British investment manager dedicated to the emerging markets. The Chairman is Peter Gibbs and the Chief Executive is Mark Coombs.[2] It had $52.6 billion under management as at 30 June 2016.[1] It is headquartered in London.[3]
Senior management[edit]
The senior management are as follows:



